paragraphs.title: Download ข้อมูล chicago bus speed
paragraphs.text:
%sh
if ! hdfs dfs -test -e "/user/zeppelin/chicago"; then
    hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /user/zeppelin/chicago
    wget https://data.cityofchicago.org/api/views/emtn-qqdi/rows.csv -O rows.csv
    hdfs dfs -put rows.csv /user/zeppelin/chicago
fi

paragraphs.title: Download ข้อมูล online store log
paragraphs.text:
%sh
if ! hdfs dfs -test -e "/user/zeppelin/accesslog"; then
    hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /user/zeppelin/accesslog
    wget  wget https://github.com/praisan/hello-world/raw/master/access.log.2.zip
    unzip access.log.2.zip
    hdfs dfs -put access.log.2 /user/zeppelin/accesslog
fi

paragraphs.title: Download ข้อมูล online store database
paragraphs.text:
%sh
if ! hdfs dfs -test -e "/user/zeppelin/retail_export"; then

    wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/praisan/hello-world/master/retail_hive_export.zip

    unzip retail_hive_export.zip
    hdfs dfs -mkdir -p /user/zeppelin/retail
    hdfs dfs -put retail_export /user/zeppelin/
fi

paragraphs.title: Download ข้อมูล OnlineRetail

%sh

paragraphs.title: put ขึ้น HDFS กรณีที่ download time out
paragraphs.text:
%sh
hdfs dfs -put rows.csv /user/zeppelin/chicago
hdfs dfs -put access.log.2 /user/zeppelin/accesslog

unzip retail_hive_export.zip
hdfs dfs -put retail_export /user/zeppelin/

unzip OnlineRetail.zip
hdfs dfs -put OnlineRetail /user/zeppelin/
